# | FRONTEND | **VITE_SKIP_AUTH**         | Optional                             | TRUE                                                                                                                                                   | Skip authentication flag               | If false and auth not configured → login breaks         | Toggle true/false → reload |
# | FRONTEND | **VITE_CHUNK_OVERLAP**     | Optional                             | 20                                                                                                                                                     | Chunk overlap size                     | Chunking quality changes                                | Adjust → process doc |
# | FRONTEND | **VITE_TOKENS_PER_CHUNK**  | Optional                             | 100                                                                                                                                                    | Tokens per chunk                       | Quality/timing changes                                  | Adjust → compare |
# | FRONTEND | **VITE_CHUNK_TO_COMBINE**  | Optional                             | 1                                                                                                                                                      | Number of chunks to combine            | Performance/quality differences                         | Adjust → process doc |
